<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8313735>
    dc:description "FIGURES 32–33. Male genitalia of Zethus in ventral view. 32, Z. angulatus; 33, Z. bakeri. crv, volsellar ridge; cu, cupis; di, digitus; go, gonocoxite; lbd, basal lobe of digitus; ldd, distal lobe of digitus." ;
