<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8313737>
    dc:description "FIGURES 34–39. Male genital structures of Zethus, 34, 36, 37, Z. angulatus; 35, 38, 39, Z. bakeri. 34 & 35, left volsella, inner view; 36 & 38, aedeagus in lateral view; 37 & 39, aedeagus in ventral view. ap, basal apodeme of aedeagus; lvv, ventral lobe of penis valve; pb, basal plate of aedeagus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8313737/files/figure.png" ;
